Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟早上起来的很早嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关灯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  真久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次分别的时候  我对你说喜欢你
